00:37:10.390 --> 00:37:15.440
is to overcome the
involuntary exclusion.

00:37:15.440 --> 00:37:20.770
So what happens is you very often
get involved in pushing for things

00:37:20.770 --> 00:37:24.670
that every other part of
you is active in opposing.

00:37:24.670 --> 00:37:28.110
And so you had a lot of people
who were against the draft

00:37:28.110 --> 00:37:35.100
in those early '70s [laughter], you
